entries.journal_entry_description: Boss Nass has suggested examining Ultragungan battle droids for clues about how to bypass the hardware security on their droids.
entries.journal_entry_title: Find the Passcode for Ultragungan Droids
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Defeat flawed Ultragungan battle droids in hope of finding the secret to bypassing the hardware protection for Ultragungan droids. Boss Nass has uploaded the location of some of the flawed battle droids, but there are other camps of them close by.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Da flawin' battle droids still had da same security measurin' as da fully functional onin', so dey didn't reveal anydin' new to ossen. Try findin' some powerin'-down battle droids. Examine dem and see what yousa can find.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Search the battle droid camps for powered-down Ultragungan battle droids to examine.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Examine Some Powered-Down Ultragungan Battle Droids
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Unfortunately, the powered-down battle droids didn't reveal anything. Even though powered off, their security features were fully functional.
entries.task03_message_box_text: Unfortunately, the powered-down battle droids didn't reveal anything. Even though powered off, their security features were fully functional.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Boss Nass. Maybe he'll have another idea.
